$ download-content-of-linked-pages.pl

`download-content-of-linked-pages.pl` is a simple (that is: rudimentary) Perl script that uses → development/languages/Perl/modules/HTML/LinkExtractor[HTML::LinkExtractor] and
→ development/languages/Perl/modules/LWP/Simple[LWP::Simple] to fetch the pages that are linked at in the document of a given → development/web/URI-URL-URN-IRI-URC#url[URL].

It is executed from the command line with
code {
$ download-content-of-linked-pages.pl https://some-host.xyz/path/to/some/file.html
code }

gh|PerlModules|/HTML/LinkExtractor/download-content-of-linked-pages.pl||
